name: Trivet LA
description: Personal Chef Service Los Angeles CA
overview:
Trivet is a healthy and hassle-free alternative to takeout and restaurant dining. In just over an hour a trained private chef Los Angeles, will prepare a delicious, healthy dinner in your home.

The meals from Trivet are healthy and child-friendly. They offer options like Lemon Garlic Herb Chicken and Tempeh Tacos. These home-made meals seem like a much better option than last minute Chinese take-out or other food delivery services in Los Angeles. Trivet also offers private chef services for two hours. This option does not include groceries, however, customers can provide chef with a recipe or chef can create a dish based on the groceries in the home. This service comes at a low rate of $40.
